fields.description:
Accessing to:
{noformat}
<yourDomainURL>/admin-api/config/<repoName>
{noformat}

Leads to an empty page. However, it works if one is accessing through using:
{noformat}
<yourDomainURL>/admin-api/config/repository/<repoName>
{noformat}

In the documentation which is accessible via "/admin-api" indicates that a repository config can be accessed via:
{noformat}
/admin-api/config/REPNAME
{noformat}
